  "description": "<ul><li>5 days (44 hours per week)</li><li>$2400 - $2700</li><li>Somerset</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Attending to customers' enquiries</li><li>Explaining the concept to guests, and educating / having conversations with them on the menu and related topics</li><li>Preparation and serving of food and drinks</li><li>Setting up and clearing down of operations</li><li>Receiving and checking of inventory and perishables</li><li>Reporting to outlet manager<br /> </li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>1-2 years’ experience and interest in F&B</li><li>Able to work weekends & public holidays</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, WA your resume to ‪‪‪+65 9136 9792‬‬‬ or email your resume to supreme.yentan@gmail.com.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>TAN YEN ZHEN (CHEN YANZHEN) REG NO: R25138932</p><p>THE SUPREMEHR ADVISORY PTE LTD EA NO: 14C7279</p>",
